## Available Commands
- `/start` - Start a session
- `/feature` - Add a feature (creates GitHub issue if MCP configured)
- `/checkpoint` - Save progress (creates PR if MCP configured)
- `/pr` - Manage pull requests
- `/sync-issues` - Sync with GitHub issues
- `/gh-status` - Show GitHub integration status
- `/merge-all` - Merge all open PRs, close issues, delete branches (in dependency order)
